Create Title for Dashboard 12

Step 1: Create blue text box background

- Insert a text box

- Select drop down under in General under Visualizations pane

- X position = 0, Y position = 0, Width = 1280, Height = 80

-Background = Color - Custom (B0C4DE)


Step 2: Create Title text box

- Insert a text box

- Choose Constantia Font, Size as 28, Bold and Centered. Type Homework Grading System.

- Select drop down under in General under Visualizations pane

- X position = 416, Y position = 0, Width = 545, Height = 62

-Background = Color - Custom (B0C4DE)
